Differencing Series to Pass the ADF Test

TotalVehicleSales <- ts(fred$series.observations(series_id = 'TOTALNSA')[,c('date','value')][,-1], 
                        start=c(1976,1), frequency = 12)
AnalyzeSeries(diff(TotalVehicleSales, differences=1))
